        <heading>953.  Legacy subject to a suspensive condition</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 953.  Legacy subject to a suspensive condition
A legacy that is subject to a suspensive condition may be accepted or renounced either before or after the fulfillment of the condition.</p>
        </content>
